I analyzed the images and message, identifying key elements: location (BGC nightlife), people involved (the user, Sean, Jeandel), the energetic and cinematic vibe, and the late-night timeline. I offered the user simple one-word options‚Äî"Generate Page 1," "Start with recovery," or "Add more day context"‚Äîto guide the next step in creating this narrative, emphasizing the event as a real, immersive story.
